data.description: Stunning home w/ great curb appeal landscaped with synthetic turf & zero scape. Upon entering this exquisite home, you will be greeted with an ample foyer, and powder room. Moving into the expansive living quarters you will enjoy an eye-catching tray ceiling, recessed lighting, beautiful dual sided gas fireplace w/ floor to ceiling tile, oversized window overlooking the backyard, and wood-look tile floors thru out the main level. Past the living room your formal dining room awaits. Enjoy the second side of your dual sided fireplace while dining with your loved ones, overlooking the large kitchen made for a chef, a large slider leads to backyard. Well-appointed kitchen w/ a huge oversized island, ample cabinet space, elegant absolute black polished granite counter tops, gas stove top, dual oven, dishwasher, walk in pantry, recessed lighting. Access to 3-car garage is located off the kitchen. Upstairs discover an open loft area. Perfect for add. living space, game room or office! Next, experience the comfort of a large sitting room adjacent to your primary bedroom, a dual sided fireplace with floor to ceiling tile accents, brings a warm & cozy feel to both the sitting room and primary bedroom. Primary is well sized, w/ recessed lighting and huge window with stunning view. Primary bath is roomy and bright w/ a dual vanity, absolute black polished granite counter tops, oversized walk-in shower w/ floor to ceiling tile, water closet, and a large walk-in closet. Down the hall are two large bedrooms, each w/ walk in closets. Laundry room located on the second floor. Large upstairs hall bathroom w/ full bath/shower combo and dual vanity with absolute black polished granite counter tops. Massive basement has been partially finished. Framing and electrical are complete, just waiting for your finishing touches. Huge backyard is landscaped with synthetic turf/zero scape, w/ a beautiful covered pergola. All of this located in the highly sought after Meridian Ranch neighborhood
